title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft  & Avionics Update - GNS 430w & GNS530w
description:
In this video we will have a look at the GNS 430w & GNS530w which received a huge update as part of the 1st beta of the Aircraft & Avionics Update for MSFS 2020. We will look at the changes being made to this avionics system and you can see clearly that the people of Working Title have been working on this one as well.
